oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jean Shepard at the Top Brass Club (16375)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Allen, Rex, 1947-; Fairchild, Barbara, 1951-; Shepard, Jean, 1933-2016; Metal photoplates; Wynette, Tammy;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Jean Shepard on June 21st, Red Allen Junior on July 4, Barbara Fairchild on July 11, and Tammy Wynette and July 26 at the Top Brass Club. Poster features metal photoplates of each artist. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/40519/rec/1.
